Modules Loaded         serial isa-pnp opl3sa2 ad1848 mpu401 sound
soundcore af_packet eepro100 unix
lines from modules.conf
options opl3sa2 io=0x220 mss_io=0x530 irq=5 dma=0 dma2=1
options sound dmabuf=1
Any suggestions?  More info can be provided if required.
Once this has happened I can't remove any of the sound modules (they're
all in use) and a reboot is the only recourse.  This all worked fine in
2.2.x
I can provide my .config or System.map if requested...
On another note I've already seen discussed here...
